@page "/FAQ"

<MudExpansionPanels MultiExpansion="true">
    <MudExpansionPanel Text="How long does it take to calculate my guilds rank?">
        Our leaderboards calculate the rank of every guild every 15 minutes at the moment.
    </MudExpansionPanel>
    <MudExpansionPanel Text="Why can't I see my character in the guild roster?">
        <MudText Typo="Typo.body1">
            This is most likely cause your character isn't level 60, at the moment we only display level 60 characters.
            If your character is level 60 and still isn't in the roster we strongly advise you report this bug<MudNavLink Href="/bugReport">here</MudNavLink>
        </MudText>   
    </MudExpansionPanel>
    <MudExpansionPanel Text="How do you calculate the rank of a guild?">
        <MudText Typo="Typo.body1">
            This information is currently not available to the public as we believe it may cause confusion among users.
            Rest assured that the rankings are exact and precise.
        </MudText>
    </MudExpansionPanel>
    <MudExpansionPanel Text="My guild isn't being added, why?">
        <MudText Typo="Typo.body1">
            If your guild has recently changed realm or undergone some sort of drastic change then this is simply on blizzards end and there is nothing we can do to help.
            If this isn't the case then please submit a bug report <MudNavLink Href="/bugReport">here</MudNavLink> 
        </MudText> 
    </MudExpansionPanel>
</MudExpansionPanels>

